  <body>

<intro>
<p>
 Associates a rescue template with a <tt>Castle.MonoRail.Framework.Controller</tt> or an action (method). The rescue is invoked in response to some exception during the action processing. 
</p>

<note>
<p>
 The view must exist in the <c>rescues</c> folder in your view folder 
</p>
</note>

</intro>



